author: ieb
msg: This commit provides XSD Validation services for the OS XSD, and creates a new Bean converter that uses XStream to perform
the Bean->XML->Bean converstion. The tests validate that the output of the serialization conforms to the the OS XSD, and the
test XML fragments are read correctly.
I have tried using BeanXStreamConverter in place of BeanXmlConverter, and seen no errors, but this patch does not replace BeanXmlConverter
just yet to let others have a chance to take a look at it.
I will continue expanding the test coverage to see that a fuller set of test patterns are used and created.
